&CP2K
 PROGRAM      Quickstep
 PROJECT      H2S
 IOLEVEL      10
 FFTLIB       FFTSG
&END

&IO
 BASIS_SET_FILE GTH_BASIS_SETS
 POTENTIAL_FILE POTENTIAL
&END

&DFT
 FUNCTIONAL   BLYP
&END

&QS
 METHOD        GAPW
 CUTOFF        240
 EXTRAPOLATION PS 3
 EPS_DEFAULT   1.0E-8
&END

&SCF
 GUESS        ATOMIC
 MAX_SCF      2
 EPS_SCF      1.0E-5
&END

&PRINT MEDIUM
&END

&KIND H
 BASIS_SET    TZV2P-GTH
 POTENTIAL    GTH-BLYP-q1
&END

&KIND S
 BASIS_SET    TZV2P-GTH
 POTENTIAL    GTH-BLYP-q6
&END

&CELL
 UNIT         ANGSTROM
 ABC          4.0  4.0  4.0
&END

&COORDS
S 0.0 0.0 0.104467
H 0.0 0.975586 -0.835734
H 0.0 -0.975586 -0.835734
&END
